caption.text: Our ethos is to unapologetically support #brands in our backyard before looking beyond. @wellscoffees has been a part of our story since day one; not just because they are #local, but because they embody #community, #craft, and #commerce in the purest form. Their product is one of the finest cups of coffee we've ever had, and keeps our members pleasantly caffeinated every single day. Wells Coffees has just launched a #kickstarter campaign to take them to the next level. They are worthy of your support. As Brandon himself once told me, "Soldier On, Friend." You're doing great things. #DrinkDeeply
